title: Justice League Collection (2008-2015)
description:
Description
This collection has the following movies:

1. Justice League: The New Frontier (2008 Video) 
2. Justice League: Crisis on Two Earths (2010 Video) 
3. Justice League: Doom (2012 Video) 
4. Justice League: The Flashpoint Paradox (2013 Video) 
5. JLA Adventures: Trapped in Time (2014 Video) 
6. Justice League: War (2014 Video)
7. Justice League: Throne of Atlantis (2015 Video) 
8. Justice League: Gods and Monsters (2015 Video)
